name: Superfast Jellyfish
wikiSummary: "Superfast Jellyfish" is the sixth track from the Gorillaz's third album Plastic Beach. It features Gruff Rhys and De La Soul. The song will be the second single from the album, due for release on May 9, 2010. The audio contains samples from a 1986 commercial for Swanson's microwave "Great Starts Breakfasts". On the Gorillaz official Youtube channel, the track has over 1 million views before the release of an official video.
